## About this folder

This folder contains a grab bag of pages used to exercise edge cases in the
MMX compiler and the folder-index generator. It is **not** user-facing
documentation; the pages here are mostly numbered stress tests (e.g.
`scrollSaveTest/00.mmx` … `50.mmx`) plus a few hand-written pages that
cover the `Getting Started` basics and nested subfolders.

If you are looking for the real docs, head back to the sidebar.
